---

<!-- TALLER DE NORMALIZACIÓN -->
<div class="p-[2px] rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 via-purple-500 to-fuchsia-500 mb-20 shadow-2xl">
  <div class="bg-zinc-900 p-10 rounded-3xl">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-violet-400">
        Taller Evaluativo · Universidad El Bosque
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 text-white">
        Taller de Normalización de BD
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-2 text-sm">
        Docente: Ing. Christian Felipe Duarte Arévalo · Bases de Datos 1
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- EJERCICIO 1 -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-violet-500/20 text-violet-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Ejercicio 1</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Tabla de Proyectos y Empleados</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Se analiza la siguiente tabla que registra la asignación de empleados a proyectos,
        identificando su forma normal actual y normalizándola hasta la 3FN.
      </p>

      <!-- Tabla 1 -->
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 mb-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-zinc-800 text-violet-300 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">cod_proyecto</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">nom_proyecto</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">cod_empleado</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">nom_empleado</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">profesion</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">vlr_hora</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">hrs_asignadas</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-800">
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">ERP</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Sandra</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Ingeniero</td><td class="px-4 py-2">100.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">20</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2 text-zinc-500">—</td><td class="px-4 py-2">ERP</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2020</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Claudia</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Analista</td><td class="px-4 py-2">50.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">10</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">ERP</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2030</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Yamyle</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Programador</td><td class="px-4 py-2">20.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">10</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1020</td><td class="px-4 py-2">CRM</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Sandra</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Ingeniero</td><td class="px-4 py-2">100.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">10</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1020</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-zinc-500">—</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2020</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Claudia</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Analista</td><td class="px-4 py-2">50.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">15</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2 text-zinc-500">—</td><td class="px-4 py-2">CRM</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2030</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Yamile</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Programador</td><td class="px-4 py-2">20.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">20</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1030</td><td class="px-4 py-2">BI</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Sandra</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Ingeniero</td><td class="px-4 py-2">100.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">10</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2 text-zinc-500">—</td><td class="px-4 py-2">BI</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2020</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Claudia</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Analista</td><td class="px-4 py-2">50.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">15</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1030</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-zinc-500">—</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2030</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Llamile</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Programador</td><td class="px-4 py-2">20.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">10</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">ERP</td><td class="px-4 py-2">2040</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Andrea</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Ingeniero</td><td class="px-4 py-2">100.000</td><td class="px-4 py-2">40</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-700">
        <p class="font-semibold text-white">Preguntas a resolver:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Indicar en qué forma normal se encuentra la tabla. Justificar la respuesta.</li>
          <li>Especificar el paso a paso para convertir la Tabla No. 1 a la <span class="text-violet-300 font-semibold">3FN</span>, mostrando cada etapa del proceso de normalización y justificando claramente cada decisión tomada.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EJERCICIO 2 -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-fuchsia-500/20 text-fuchsia-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Ejercicio 2</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Tabla de Estudiantes — 1NF</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Análisis de la tabla de estudiantes para determinar si cumple la Primera Forma Normal
        y rediseño de las tablas resultantes si es necesario.
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 mb-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-zinc-800 text-fuchsia-300 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Cod</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Name</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Email</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Courses</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">GradePoints</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-800">
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">100111</td><td class="px-4 py-2">John Doe</td><td class="px-4 py-2">doe@usna.edu</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-amber-400">NN204, SI204, IT221</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-amber-400">2, 3, 3</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">092244</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Matt Smith</td><td class="px-4 py-2">smith@usna.edu</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-amber-400">SM223, EE301</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-amber-400">4, 4</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">113221</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Melinda Black</td><td class="px-4 py-2">black@usna.edu</td><td class="px-4 py-2">SI204</td><td class="px-4 py-2">3</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">090112</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Tom Johnson</td><td class="px-4 py-2">johnson@usna.edu</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-amber-400">NN204, SI204, IT221</td><td class="px-4 py-2 text-amber-400">4, 2, 3</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30 rounded-xl p-4 mb-4 text-sm text-amber-200">
        <span class="text-amber-400 font-bold mt-0.5">⚠</span>
        <p>Las columnas <strong>Courses</strong> y <strong>GradePoints</strong> contienen valores multivaluados (múltiples cursos y notas en una sola celda), lo que viola la 1NF.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-700">
        <p class="font-semibold text-white">Preguntas a resolver:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>¿La tabla de Estudiantes está en 1NF? ¿Por qué?</li>
          <li>Si no está en 1NF, rediseñar las tablas resultantes indicando nombre de tabla, columnas, llaves primarias y llaves foráneas.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EJERCICIO 3 -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-pink-500/20 text-pink-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Ejercicio 3</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Restaurante — Cenas de Empresa (Member_Dinner)</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        El gerente del restaurante nocturno necesita un sistema para planificar cenas y
        registrar asistencia. La clave primaria de la tabla es <span class="text-pink-300 font-mono text-xs bg-zinc-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">Número de miembro + Número de cena</span>.
        Las cenas pueden tener múltiples platos.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-700">
        <p class="font-semibold text-white">Preguntas a resolver:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Analizar si existe algún valor multivaluado. Justificar la respuesta.</li>
          <li>Plantear el esquema relacional con nombre de tabla <span class="text-pink-300 font-semibold">"Member_Dinner"</span>.</li>
          <li>Elaborar el diagrama de dependencias funcionales para la 1FN.</li>
          <li>Convertir el resultado a la <span class="text-pink-300 font-semibold">3FN</span> paso a paso, justificando cada decisión tomada.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EJERCICIO 4 -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Ejercicio 4</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Tabla de Visitas Médicas</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Análisis de la tabla de visitas médicas para identificar su forma normal y convertirla a 3FN,
        utilizando las dependencias funcionales provistas.
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 mb-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-zinc-800 text-indigo-300 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">VisitaNo</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">DiaVisita</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">PacNo</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">PacEdad</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">PacCiudad</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">ProvNo</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">ProvEspecialidad</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Diagnostico</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-800 text-xs">
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">V10020</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1/13/2019</td><td class="px-4 py-2">P1</td><td class="px-4 py-2">35</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Bogotá</td><td class="px-4 py-2">D1</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Internista</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Infección de oído</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">V10020</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1/13/2019</td><td class="px-4 py-2">P1</td><td class="px-4 py-2">35</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Bogotá</td><td class="px-4 py-2">D2</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Prac. Enfermería</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Influenza</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">V93030</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1/20/2019</td><td class="px-4 py-2">P3</td><td class="px-4 py-2">17</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Cali</td><td class="px-4 py-2">D2</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Prac. Enfermería</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Embarazo</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">V82110</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1/18/2019</td><td class="px-4 py-2">P2</td><td class="px-4 py-2">60</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Cúcuta</td><td class="px-4 py-2">D3</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Cardiólogo</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Soplo cardíaco</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Dependencias funcionales -->
      <div class="bg-zinc-800/60 rounded-xl p-5 mb-5 border border-indigo-500/20">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 mb-3 font-semibold">Dependencias Funcionales</p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2 font-mono text-xs text-zinc-300">
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg px-3 py-2">PacNo → PacEdad, PacCiudad</div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg px-3 py-2">ProvNo → ProvEspecialidad</div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg px-3 py-2">VisitaNo → PacNo, DiaVisita, PacEdad, PacCiudad</div>
          <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg px-3 py-2">VisitaNo, ProvNo → Diagnóstico</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-700">
        <p class="font-semibold text-white">Preguntas a resolver:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Indicar y justificar en qué forma normal se encuentra la tabla.</li>
          <li>Especificar el esquema relacional de la Tabla No. 2.</li>
          <li>Plantear el diagrama de dependencias funcionales.</li>
          <li>Convertir la tabla a <span class="text-indigo-300 font-semibold">3FN</span> paso a paso, justificando cada decisión.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EJERCICIO 5 -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Ejercicio 5</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Netflix DVD Rentals — 3FN y BCNF</h3>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Análisis de la tabla de alquileres de DVD de Netflix. La llave primaria es la clave compuesta
        <span class="text-cyan-300 font-mono text-xs bg-zinc-800 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">(RentalID, Title)</span>.
        El objetivo es descomponer la tabla hasta 3FN y evaluar cambios hacia BCNF.
      </p>

      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 mb-6">
        <table class="w-full text-sm text-zinc-300">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-zinc-800 text-cyan-300 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">RentalID</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Title</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">CustomerID</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">MailedOutDate</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Director</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">MovieCategory</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Price</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-zinc-800 text-xs">
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Die Hard</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1001</td><td class="px-4 py-2">3/3/2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">John McTiernan</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Old</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$4.25</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1</td><td class="px-4 py-2">The Last Man Standing</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1001</td><td class="px-4 py-2">3/3/2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Walter Hill</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Old</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$4.25</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">1</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Wedding Crashers</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1001</td><td class="px-4 py-2">3/3/2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">David Dobkin</td><td class="px-4 py-2">New</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$5.50</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">2</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Dodgeball</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1002</td><td class="px-4 py-2">3/4/2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Rawson Marshall Thurber</td><td class="px-4 py-2">New</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$5.50</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">2</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Die Hard</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1002</td><td class="px-4 py-2">3/4/2010</td><td class="px-4 py-2">John McTiernan</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Old</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$4.25</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">3</td><td class="px-4 py-2">As Good as It Gets</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1003</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1/7/2011</td><td class="px-4 py-2">James Brooks</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Old</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$4.25</td></tr>
            <tr class="hover:bg-zinc-800/50"><td class="px-4 py-2">4</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Forrest Gump</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1001</td><td class="px-4 py-2">1/7/2011</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Robert Zemeckis</td><td class="px-4 py-2">Old</td><td class="px-4 py-2">$4.25</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-700">
        <p class="font-semibold text-white">Preguntas a resolver:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>¿Es verdadera la dependencia funcional <span class="font-mono text-cyan-300 text-xs">RentalID → CustomerID</span>? ¿Y <span class="font-mono text-cyan-300 text-xs">Director → Title</span>? Justificar.</li>
          <li>Plantear el esquema relacional de la tabla <span class="text-cyan-300 font-semibold">"Rentals"</span>.</li>
          <li>Especificar las dependencias funcionales pertinentes.</li>
          <li>Plantear el diagrama de dependencias funcionales para la 1FN.</li>
          <li>Descomponer "Rentals" en tablas que estén en <span class="text-cyan-300 font-semibold">3FN</span>, indicando nombre, columnas, llaves primarias y foráneas.</li>
          <li>¿En qué cambiaría la descomposición para llegar a <span class="text-cyan-300 font-semibold">BCNF</span>? Mostrar el resultado y justificar.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- EJERCICIO 6 — REFLEXIÓN -->
    <div class="mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-rose-500/20 text-rose-300 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Ejercicio 6</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Reflexión: Diseño E-R y Normalización</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-800/40 rounded-xl p-6 border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
